tip.text: The "Buckhead Express" lunch is an excellent choice for anyone!! Comes with soup or salad, a meat dish and an iced tea or soda.
Blackened swordfish pita is very good. The chips with the pita look home-made and non greasy :)
Both Chili and white pepper crabs are good. Service is good too. Look forward to coming back again.
Aside from the horrible hot chocolate, I have to say the pastries are very good. Love the fruit tart. Will be back to try the creme brûlée. Oh.. The service is good too, nothing to complain about.
Been to Paul at London and Paris, the hot chocolate in Singapore is very disappointing. Too rich and for someone who drinks hot chocolate at least twice a wk, this just simply does not made the cut.
Love the pastries too!! There is so far nothing I do not like at Antoinette :D

Excellent service and love the food!! The French toast with caramelized bananas is made to perfection. I never know French toast can taste so good! My personal choice of beverage is the chamomile tea.
